{"title_page": "Parada do Monte", "text_new": "{{Infobox Portuguese subdivision \n|type = parish \n|official_name      = Parada do Monte\n|image_skyline      = \n|image_caption      = \n|image_flag         =\n|image_shield       = \n|image_location     = Parada do Monte Melgaco.png\n|region             = [[Norte Region, Portugal|Norte]]\n|CIM                = [[Alto Minho]]\n|district           = [[Viana do Castelo District|Viana do Castelo]]\n|municipality       = [[Melga\u00e7o, Portugal|Melga\u00e7o]]\n|coordinates        = {{coord|42|02|32|N|8|15|56|W|source:ptwiki_region:PT_type:city|display=it}}\n|elevation          =\n|area_total         = 27.32\n|population_as_of   = \n|population_total   = 487\n|patron             =\n|area_code          = \n|postal_code        = \n|website            = \n|dissolved          = 2013\n}}\n'''Parada do Monte''' is a former [[Freguesia (Portugal)|civil parish]] in the municipality of [[Melga\u00e7o, Portugal|Melga\u00e7o]] in the [[Viana do Castelo District]], Portugal. In 2013, the parish merged into the new parish [[Parada do Monte e Cubalh\u00e3o]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Law nr. 11-A/2013, page 552 70|url=http://dre.pt/pdf1sdip/2013/01/01901/0000200147.pdf |accessdate=28 July 2014|author=''[[Di\u00e1rio da Rep\u00fablica]]''|language=Portuguese|format=pdf}}</ref> It has a population of 487 inhabitants and a total area of 27.32&nbsp;km\u00b2.<ref>[http://www.cm-melgaco.pt/portal/page/melgaco/portal_municipal/municipio/municipio_freguesias/ParadadoMonte C\u00e2mara Municipal de Melga\u00e7o]</ref>\n<ref>[http://www.cm-melgaco.pt/portal/page/melgaco/portal_municipal/municipio/municipio_dadosestatisticos/municipio_estatistica_Demografia Demographics of Melga\u00e7o] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718083225/http://www.cm-melgaco.pt/portal/page/melgaco/portal_municipal/municipio/municipio_dadosestatisticos/municipio_estatistica_Demografia |date=2011-07-18 }}</ref>\n\n[[File:Parada do Monte Church.JPG|thumb|200px|left|Parada do Monte Church]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Parishes of Melga\u00e7o, Portugal]]\n\n\n{{VianadoCastelo-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Portuguese subdivision \n|type = parish \n|official_name      = Parada do Monte\n|image_skyline      = \n|image_caption      = \n|image_flag         =\n|image_shield       = \n|image_location     = Parada do Monte Melgaco.png\n|region             = [[Norte Region, Portugal|Norte]]\n|CIM                = [[Alto Minho]]\n|district           = [[Viana do Castelo District|Viana do Castelo]]\n|municipality       = [[Melga\u00e7o, Portugal|Melga\u00e7o]]\n|coordinates        = {{coord|42|02|32|N|8|15|56|W|source:ptwiki_region:PT_type:city|display=it}}\n|elevation          =\n|area_total         = 27.32\n|population_as_of   = \n|population_total   = 487\n|patron             =\n|area_code          = \n|postal_code        = \n|website            = \n|dissolved          = 2013\n}}\n'''Parada do Monte''' is a former [[Freguesia (Portugal)|civil parish]] in the municipality of [[Melga\u00e7o, Portugal|Melga\u00e7o]] in the [[Viana do Castelo District]], Portugal. In 2013, the parish merged into the new parish [[Parada do Monte e Cubalh\u00e3o]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Law nr. 11-A/2013, page 552 70|url=http://dre.pt/pdf1sdip/2013/01/01901/0000200147.pdf |accessdate=28 July 2014|author=''[[Di\u00e1rio da Rep\u00fablica]]''|language=Portuguese|format=pdf}}</ref> It has a population of 487 inhabitants and a total area of 27.32&nbsp;km\u00b2.<ref>[http://www.cm-melgaco.pt/portal/page/melgaco/portal_municipal/municipio/municipio_freguesias/ParadadoMonte C\u00e2mara Municipal de Melga\u00e7o]</ref>\n<ref>[http://www.cm-melgaco.pt/portal/page/melgaco/portal_municipal/municipio/municipio_dadosestatisticos/municipio_estatistica_Demografia Demographics of Melga\u00e7o] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718083225/http://www.cm-melgaco.pt/portal/page/melgaco/portal_municipal/municipio/municipio_dadosestatisticos/municipio_estatistica_Demografia |date=2011-07-18 }}</ref>\n\n[[File:Parada do Monte Church.JPG|thumb|200px|left|Parada do Monte Church]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Parishes of Melga\u00e7o, Portugal]]\n\n\n{{VianadoCastelo-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parada_do_Monte"}
{"title_page": "Parada de Gonta", "text_new": "{{Infobox Portuguese subdivision \n|type = parish \n|official_name      = Parada de Gonta\n|image_skyline      = \n|image_caption      = \n|image_flag         =\n|image_shield       = \n|image_location     = \n|region             = [[Centro Region, Portugal|Centro]]\n|CIM                = [[Viseu D\u00e3o Laf\u00f5es]]\n|district           = [[Viseu District|Viseu]]\n|municipality       = [[Tondela]]\n|coordinates        = {{coord|40.582|-7.996|type:adm1st_region:PT_dim:50000|display=inline,title}}\n|elevation          =\n|area_total         = 6.73\n|population_as_of   = 2011\n|population_total   = 754\n|patron             =\n|area_code          = \n|postal_code        = \n|website            = http://paradadegonta.org\n}}\n'''Parada de Gonta''' is a [[Portugal|Portuguese]] [[Freguesia|parish]] of the [[Municipalities of Portugal|municipality]] of [[Tondela Municipality|Tondela]]. The population in 2011 was 754,<ref name=ine>[http://www.ine.pt/ngt_server/attachfileu.jsp?look_parentBoui=165404348&att_display=n&att_download=y Instituto Nacional de Estat\u00edstica (INE)], Census 2011 results according to the 2013 administrative division of Portugal</ref> in an area of 6.73&nbsp;km\u00b2.<ref name=dgt>[http://www.dgterritorio.pt/cartografia_e_geodesia/cartografia/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal_caop_/caop__download_/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal___versao_2017__em_vigor_/ \u00c1reas das freguesias, concelhos, distritos e pa\u00eds]</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Parishes of Tondela]]\n[[Category:Populated places in Viseu District]]\n\n\n{{Viseu-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Portuguese subdivision \n|type = parish \n|official_name      = Parada de Gonta\n|image_skyline      = \n|image_caption      = \n|image_flag         =\n|image_shield       = \n|image_location     = \n|region             = [[Centro Region, Portugal|Centro]]\n|CIM                = [[Viseu D\u00e3o Laf\u00f5es]]\n|district           = [[Viseu District|Viseu]]\n|municipality       = [[Tondela]]\n|coordinates        = {{coord|40.582|-7.996|type:adm1st_region:PT_dim:50000|display=inline,title}}\n|elevation          =\n|area_total         = 6.73\n|population_as_of   = 2011\n|population_total   = 754\n|patron             =\n|area_code          = \n|postal_code        = \n|website            = http://paradadegonta.org\n}}\n'''Parada de Gonta''' is a [[Portugal|Portuguese]] [[Freguesia|parish]] of the [[Municipalities of Portugal|municipality]] of [[Tondela Municipality|Tondela]]. The population in 2011 was 754,<ref name=ine>[http://www.ine.pt/ngt_server/attachfileu.jsp?look_parentBoui=165404348&att_display=n&att_download=y Instituto Nacional de Estat\u00edstica (INE)], Census 2011 results according to the 2013 administrative division of Portugal</ref> in an area of 6.73&nbsp;km\u00b2.<ref name=dgt>[http://www.dgterritorio.pt/cartografia_e_geodesia/cartografia/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal_caop_/caop__download_/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal___versao_2017__em_vigor_/ \u00c1reas das freguesias, concelhos, distritos e pa\u00eds]</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Parishes of Tondela]]\n[[Category:Populated places in Viseu District]]\n\n\n{{Viseu-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parada_de_Gonta"}
