9>\n{{cite web\n |last1=Jewitt |first1=D.\n |last2=Weaver |first2=H. A.\n |last3=Mutchler |first3=M.\n |last4=Agarwal |first4=J.\n |last5=Kim |first5=Y.\n |last6=Hui |first6=M.-T.\n |date=25 September 2019\n |title=Proposal 16009 - Interstellar Object C/2019 Q4\n |url=http://www.stsci.edu/hst/phase2-public/16009.pdf\n |access-date=27 September 2019\n |publisher=Space Telescope Science Institute\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=NYT-20191001>\n{{cite news\n|last=Overbye\n|first=Dennis\n|authorlink=Dennis Overbye\n|title=An Interstellar Comet, in Time for the Holidays - On Dec. 7, the extrasolar comet now known as 2I/Borisov will make its closest approach to the sun.\n|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/10/01/science/interstellar-comet-astronomy-borisov.html\n|date=1 October 2019\n|work=[[The New York Times]]\n|accessdate=2 October 2019\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Hubble100719>\n{{Citation\n |publisher=Space Telescope Science Institute\n |url=http://www.stsci.edu/ftp/observing/weekly_timeline/timeline_10_07_19\n |date=7 October 2019\n |title=HST Weekly Observing Timeline\n |access-date=8 October 2019\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=EA-20191014>{{cite web\n|author=Astronomical Observatory, Jagiellonian University\n|title=Interstellar Comet with a Familiar Look\n|url=https://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2019-10/aoju-icw101119.php\n|date=14 October 2019\n|work=[[EurekAlert!]]\n|accessdate=14 October 2014\n|author-link=Jagiellonian University\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Siegel2017>\n{{cite web\n |last=Siegel |first=Ethan\n |title=Ask Ethan: Why Don't Comets Orbit The Same Way Planets Do?\n |url=https://medium.com/starts-with-a-bang/ask-ethan-why-dont-comets-orbit-the-same-way-planets-do-75872f5d5ec0\n |date=16 December 2017\n |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191001175343/https://medium.com/starts-with-a-bang/ask-ethan-why-dont-comets-orbit-the-same-way-planets-do-75872f5d5ec0\n |archive-date=1 October 2019\n |url-status=live\n |accessdate=1 October 2019\n}}</ref>\n\n}} <!-- end of reflist-->\n\n== External links ==\n* {{JPL small body|id=1003639}}\n* [https://news.yale.edu/sites/default/files/styles/featured_media/public/comet-side-by-side.jpg?itok=SqC8WoFN&c=07307e7d6a991172b9f808eb83b18804 Image of 2I/Borisov] \u2013 [https://news.yale.edu/2019/11/26/new-image-offers-close-view-interstellar-comet comet is \"14 times the size of Earth\"] ([[Yale University]]; November 2019)\n* [https://www.gemini.edu/node/21240 Image of 2I/Borisov] from the [[Gemini Observatory]], Hawaii\n* [http://lesia.obspm.fr/comets/lib/display-all-pict.php?Code=CK19Q040&Username=&CodeObs=&Config=&y1=2019&m1=08&y2=2021&m2=10&typ=pict Pictures of 2I/Borisov] from [[Paris Observatory#Meudon|Paris Observatory (LESIA)]]\n* [https://in-space.ru/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/gb00234.gif Discovery animation]\n* [https://projectpluto.com/temp/2i.htm FAQ] at ProjectPluto (Bill Gray)\n* [http://exoplanet.eu/catalog/2i/borisov Extrasolar Planetary Encyclopedia] \u2013 2I/Borisov\n* [http://orbitsimulator.com/gravitySimulatorCloud/simulations/1568147419153_gb00234.html Hyperbolic orbit simulation] \u2013 2I/Borisov (Tony Dunn)\n* [https://minorplanetcenter.net/mpec/K19/K19TB6.html Minor Planet Center] MPEC 2019-T116 : COMET 2I/Borisov\n* [http://aerith.net/comet/catalog/0002I/mag.gif Magnitude plot] by Seiichi Yoshida @ aerith.net (with predicted brightness)\n* {{youtube|C1IVdfFSPww|Video (31:13) \u2013 2I/Borisov talk}} (MBusch/[[Seth Shostak|SShostak]]) \u2013 [[SETI]] (19 September 2019)\n* {{youtube|NNOb3xrjOhE|Video (02:07) \u2013 2I/Borisov chemical composition}} \u2013 [[NASA]] (20 April 2020)\n* {{youtube|vqMJo3DHOfg|Video (01:00) \u2013 2I/Borisov orbit animations}}\n{{2019 in space}}\n{{Comets}}\n\n[[Category:Astronomical objects discovered in 2019|20190830]]\n[[Category:Comets in 2019]]\n[[Category:Discoveries by amateur astronomers]]\n[[Category:Discoveries by the Crimean Astrophysical Observatory]]\n[[Category:Hyperbolic comets]]\n[[Category:Interstellar objects]]\n[[Category:Milky